   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>From the <uicontrol>Main Menu</uicontrol>, select <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Settings</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Date and time</uicontrol>
               </menucascade> using the UP/DOWN keys and the ENTER key. You can press
the ESC key at any time to cancel the modification of the parameter
values.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <table outputclass="font:10">
                  <tgroup cols="1">
                     <colspec colname="col1"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>
                              <screen xml:space="preserve">Date and Time:Date:   21-Jul-2015Time:   11:35:08</screen>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Press the ENTER key to start modifying the parameter values.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <table outputclass="font:10">
                  <tgroup cols="1">
                     <colspec colname="col1"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>
                              <screen xml:space="preserve">Date and Time:Date:  ↕21-Jul-2015Time:   11:35:08        SET</screen>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Press the UP/DOWN keys to modify the parameter values and
press the ENTER key to confirm modification and move to the next parameter
value.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <table outputclass="font:10">
                  <tgroup cols="1">
                     <colspec colname="col1"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>
                              <screen xml:space="preserve">Date and Time:Date:   22↕Jul-2015Time:   11:35:08        SET</screen>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>When you have modified all the parameter values, the cursor
will point to <uicontrol>SET</uicontrol> – press the ENTER
key to confirm and save the modified date and time values.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <table outputclass="font:10">
                  <tgroup cols="1">
                     <colspec colname="col1"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
